complexity of the request and the number of responsive documents. A request that results in no responsive documents may nonetheless incur a fee. See the OSTP FOIA Handbook for more information about submitting a FOIA request, response timing, fee structures and waivers. OSTP FOIA Library OSTP FOIA Handbook – March 2013 [PDF] Final Rule: OSTP’s Implementation of FOIA OSTP’s Designation of a Chief FOIA Officer [PDF] OSTP Final Guidelines for Ensuring the Quality of Disseminated Information (Oct. 1, 2002) [PDF] OSTP FOIA Reports 2020 Q2 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2020 Q2 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2020 Q1 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2020 Q1 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2020 Chief FOIA Officer Report 2019 FOIA Annual Report (PDF) 2019 FOIA Annual Report (xml) 2019 OSTP FOIA Raw Data Report 2019 Q4 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2019 Q4 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2019 Q3 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2019 Q3 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2019 Q2 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2019 Q2 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2019 Q1 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2019 Q1 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2018 OSTP Final FOIA Raw Data Report 2018 FOIA Annual Report (xml) 2018 FOIA Annual Report (PDF) 2018 Q4 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2018 Q4 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2018 Chief FOIA Officer Report (PDF) 2018 Q3 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2018 Q3 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2018 Q2 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2018 Q2 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2018 Q1 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2018 Q1 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2017 OSTP Final Report (PDF) 2017 OSTP Final Report Raw Data 2017 OSTP Chief FOIA Officer Report (PDF) 2017 Q4 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2017 Q4 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2017 Q3 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2017 Q3 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2017 Q2 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2017 Q2 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2017 Q1 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2017 Q1 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2016 OSTP FOIA Report (xml) 2016 OSTP FOIA Report (PDF) 2016 OSTP Final Report Raw Data OSTP’s FOIA reports from 2004-2016 OSTP Visitor Logs March 2020 February 2020 January 2020 December 2019 November 2019 October 2019 September 2019 August